body: Ofuda-sensei artwork is really blissful. I keep laughing when Kitakami got rejuvenated from her original from. But still, cute indeed. 100/10 would be added as my favorite.
Not my very favorite Ohuda work, but still some adorable expressions. Glad I made Hennojin do this one, even if it took almost a year to get around to releasing.
Unfortunately the cover is the best part of it
